OL,3,CThree men convicted of murder could
OL,4,Cclear their names
OL,6,FThree men have had their murder
OL,7,Fconvictions referred to the Court of
OL,8,FAppeal after a review of new evidence
OL,9,Fand arguments which undermine the
OL,10,F'gang narrative' relied on by the
OL,11,Fprosecution at trial.
OL,13,FDurrell Goodall, Reano Walters and
OL,14,FTrey Wilson, who were 20, 19 and 19
OL,15,Fwhen they were convicted, were jailed
OL,16,Fin August 2017 for the joint
OL,17,Fenterprise murder of Abdul Hafidah,
OL,18,F18, in Moss Side, Manchester in May
OL,19,F2016.
