OL,3,CThree men convicted of murder could
OL,4,Cclear their names
OL,6,FMr Hafidah died from two stab wounds
OL,7,Fto the neck and injuries to his head
OL,8,Ftwo days after he was kicked, stabbed,
OL,9,Fattacked with a hammer and hit by a
OL,10,Fcar in May 2016.
OL,12,FAll three men were sentenced to life
OL,13,Fat a second trial.
OL,15,FThe Criminal Cases Review Commission
OL,16,F(CCRC) says it has now reviewed new
OL,17,Fevidence, including multiple expert
OL,18,Freports criticising the prosecution's
OL,19,Ftrial evidence.
