OL,3,CThree men convicted of murder could
OL,4,Cclear their names
OL,6,FIt said expert reports note the lack
OL,7,Fof defence argument around gang
OL,8,Fnarrative and criticise the judge's
OL,9,Fdirections to the jury on the same
OL,10,Ftheme.
OL,12,FThe review of evidence, the CCRC says,
OL,13,Fdetermined that there is a real
OL,14,Fpossibility the Court of Appeal will
OL,15,Ffind the fresh evidence "undermines
OL,16,Fthe prosecution case at trial in a key
OL,17,Fway, which may have significantly
OL,18,Fimpacted the jury's conclusions."
