OL,3,CThree men convicted of murder could
OL,4,Cclear their names
OL,6,FCCRC Chair Dame Vera Baird KC said:
OL,7,F"This referral highlights the need for
OL,8,Fsafeguards to protect defendants
OL,9,Fagainst the risk of unfairness from a
OL,10,Ftoo readily adopted gang narrative,
OL,11,Fbased on inappropriate labelling.
OL,13,F"It is possible that there are other
OL,14,Fcases which would benefit from
OL,15,Fguidance on this issue, where the fear
OL,16,Fmay be that stereotypes can be wrongly
OL,17,Fintroduced as evidence."
